<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Daily Aarti and Pooja | Live Temple Darshan & Spiritual Insights</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Experience daily aarti and pooja rituals, live temple darshan, and spiritual guidance to enrich your soul.">
